name: Onegaii
overview:
Onegaii is a virtual personal assistant service that provides time-saving, cost-efficient services for entrepreneurs, startups, business organizations and busy executives.

Onegaii offers a range of value adding services including contact management, social media management, market/internet research and data analysis, proofreading/copy editing/copy writing/blog writing, calendar and travel scheduling, and design services (squeeze pages, web and graphic design, press kits, one-sheets, brochures) and more.

The company is headquartered in the San Francisco Bay Area and provides services for clients around the country.
